messageBody:
Hi All,

I'm making progress with QS, and enjoying it.

I tried openening the "texts" in the files, but I do not have Quick
View, which is required to open them.

Does anyone have some texts written in Junior that they are willing
to send me in Word via e-mail as an attachement? I really need the
reading excersise.

I appreciate your help.

Thanks,
Chris
